The Taxi
driver was driving recklessly passing vehicles on the yellow line. One of the Tshwane
Metro Police officers spotted by the taxi driver and pulled him over. When he was
stopped the officer was issuing him with a fine, then he tried to bribe the cop. “The
officer also noticed that he was sitting with a can of alcohol between his legs,”
said Arrive Alive. He was then
arrested for drinking and driving, bribery and reckless driving He is
expected to appear in court soon.